race.description: Silks Under The Stars 23 Jan Class 4 Handicap
race.comment: HEYOKA (5) has placed two from two around this circuit and rarely puts in a poor performance. Looks well treated with the added aid of the claim and rates as the leading contender in this line-up. ATELIER (8) brings NSW formlines to the table and any market confidence must be noted. The well-related ROCK HARD LOVE (4) (full to G3 winner Parry Sound) is one from one over this course and distance and is capable of featuring prominently. AMBASSADORS (7) led throughout first up at Ipswich. Tried the same there last start however just faded late. From the low draw will again go forward and be prominent throughout.
